  "body": "### Description\r\nType: UI Fixes\r\n\r\nSummary: We are introducing UI fixes in order to improve the design and increase readability of the chat area.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\nUI fixes include:\r\n- New open source font [Inter UI](https://rsms.me/inter/). Note that this font will eventually be used across other Status products (mobile, desktop, websites)\r\n- Adjusted paddings and line heights to improve readability\r\n- Alignment of elements\r\n- Ability to select text (current bug) and its style\r\n- Show timestamps only onHover\r\n\r\n### Current implementation\r\n\r\n<img width=\"819\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-10-24 a la s 12 35 03 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/47424971-4309b080-d789-11e8-9496-965a739adf31.png\">\r\n\r\n### Design with fixes\r\n\r\n<img width=\"516\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-12-03 a la s 11 27 35 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/49379684-7a576f80-f6ee-11e8-8915-d374abf4c57a.png\">\r\n\r\n[Design on Figma + guidelines](https://www.figma.com/file/MRYBI5axcTwL4Ft8xAYhFOfy/Desktop?node-id=134%3A1887) \r\n\r\n**Please, share your implementation with the team before merging, so we can find bugs together before they are exposed to a broader audience** ðŸ˜Š \r\n",
